Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いったい何が正解なんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}タイムラインに咲き乱れるFAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:33.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:38.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絶望や歓喜なんて  駆け抜けるだけのMirage
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溢れるインフォメーション  揺らいでいるノンフィクション
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:44.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赤い冷静  青い情熱  曖昧な審判（ジャッジ）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見透かしちゃうジーザス飼い馴らし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:47.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無関心ヴィーナス気取ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷走幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:56.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溺れていたいんでしょ  妄想はいつだって蜜の味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:02.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃ物足んないなら…「本能」（はだ）を曝せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:05.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さぁ、Naked  Dive！感情を放って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確かめろ君のREALを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう、Naked  Dive！衝動のMyself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:14.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求め続ければいいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:17.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  無我夢中で叫べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:20.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  限界はないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  その真理（こたえ）の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:27.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  拓けNew  world！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————OPCN————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}究竟何為正解？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在時間線上爭奇鬥豔的虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:33.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:38.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕望和歡喜  只不過是穿插而過的幻景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滿溢而出的資訊  搖搖欲墜的認知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:44.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紅色代表冷靜  藍色代表熱情  這曖昧不清的判定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掌控洞悉一切的耶穌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:47.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假冒冰冷美豔的維納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷茫幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:56.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要沉溺於其中吧  妄想無論何時都如蜜之味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:02.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若是還不夠的話…那就把「本能」都展現出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:05.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧  Naked  Dive！  將感情釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去確定屬於你的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯  Naked  Dive！  不斷追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:14.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}屬於自己內心的那份衝動不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:17.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  盡情地呼喊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:20.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  沒有任何界限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  邁向那片真理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:27.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  開拓新的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为意识和记忆被enigma夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所留下的后遗症让她一直处于昏迷状态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不封印enigma的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会醒过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我之前告诉你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有在这个研究所帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要是有什么情况  会立刻联系你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑中的enigma昨日又袭击了3名能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今为止至少有30名左右的能力者受害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在硬撑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不但久别重逢的妈妈是phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己的能力都被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心一定很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是晴彦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  能在这见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你母亲现在的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你母亲相识大概是在2年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她之前的事我并没有详细询问过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  可以看出有着相当复杂的隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  她看上去吃了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你母亲每天都深情望着的书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打开看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直都很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又觉得事到如今已没脸再见你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被那份罪恶感所折磨着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在心里舒服点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来就去探望露露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  住手  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  买布丁带给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您母亲身体状况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…还没有什么改善
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直都这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她能早日康复
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和我们一起去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  岂敢岂敢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的人跟去的话  只会添乱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我去准备大麦茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大麦茶可是{\3c&H680B88&\4c&H2D042B&}希波克拉底{\r}也经常喝的健康饮料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:49.53,TIPS1,NTP,0,0,0,,希波克拉底是古希腊伯里克利时代的医师，西方医学奠基人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据他的书中记载
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先将大麦炒制  然后用大约3公升的水…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停  停  你偏题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  没注意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露她这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就像是晴彦哥哥一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma又没对她做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会和你的特异能力被夺走有关？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为露露和晴彦你关系非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因此受到了影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我们一直在一起  但真会影响到她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让诸位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就来给各位倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露  我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么行  我来倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  能知道enigma在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有什么情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们也没有得知任何情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层似乎在极力隐瞒着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的露露也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  洒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是个小冒失鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  一脸凝重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个修好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么  小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报被隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了连接阿赖耶识社的服务器而造的专用通讯设备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用这个入侵服务器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尽可能多知道些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然是无法打败enigma的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要修的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它之前也替我爸爸修好了电脑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不不  就算如此也不可能那么顺利就修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  还会入侵服务器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止的辛苦究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事要是被发现就惨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是放着不管的话  到时候就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报被隐瞒了是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是普通的phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了  阿尔布雷希特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强化phantom  enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强化phantom…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿赖耶识社从以前开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就将收集来的特异能力者的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按不同学校进行储存并分析
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在进行人工强化phantom的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人工强化？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是对抓来的phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又进行人类遗传因子的编入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又加以科学的处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和原来的phantom是完全两种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用途是低成本的劳动力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军事中使用的人造士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及药品实验的实验体之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些可怕的想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有保护phantom的法律存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是enigma拥有了远超研究者预想的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后变得藐视人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动了叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方区域限制入内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出示入内许可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是回自己的老家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以并不需要什么许可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说明您的来意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会帮您联系相关部门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿赖耶识社对于这次的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎打算装不知情到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起phantom  这些家伙要恶劣得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  这里也有我们的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姬野老师上传的数据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于赫塞亚学院特异能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条晴彦和妖精型phantom露露的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是晴彦和我的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿赖耶识社的研究设施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许再靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对人类没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的只是这个研究设施里的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退避  退避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面很危险  请不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来由我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么可能丢下失去能力的你自己走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  你耍什么帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家那么担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去当然是一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  阿尔布雷希特一定能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你明白大家的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白个屁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从后门过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma的目标是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存放在研究所和医院的phantom的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma得到了一条的召唤能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要有数据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能随心所欲操纵phantom了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是变成那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  enigma的最终目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配phantom  征服人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma不断袭击特异能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更为强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先得尽快把患者疏散避难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要着急  慢慢地走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事态好严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个也有被夺走能力的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是避免和enigma接触
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去帮助疏导人群吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算先攻击医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以  避难还没完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能让现在的你去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还有我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  你们快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  来了几个熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你是打算成为Phantom的女王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王  这称呼真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  征服所有的人类和Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是只有我才能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是被人类创造出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我是被人类创造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是作为实验材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身上下都被摆弄  改造了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被变成了一个既不是人类也不是Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和任何生物都不同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才记恨人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有  我可是很感谢他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能以Phantom之身使用人类的异能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我超越了Phantom与人类这两者的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经站在了进化的顶端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落后服从先进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的能力我也收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气解决她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  封住她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我来拿走你们的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  连你都跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用这模样解决你吧  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就让你解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真帅气  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈我很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还有办法能恢复你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你仔细听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一条你的身上诞生出的Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都关注着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而得出了这个结论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露也许就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条你下意识中所压抑的豪放性格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实体化所形成的Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  露露体内也会拥有你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且可能与你一起同步共同成长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:59.61,English,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1078.001,960)}synchronize
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个能力我也一起拿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把保存在露露体内的能力移到一条身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可具体怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做和enigma夺取能力时一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快做啊  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  没时间考虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和晴彦…这实在太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害羞个什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连玲奈你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说  快做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我在这里  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们休想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我们的内心世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快些找到保存的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  下手重了点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是再被我夺走一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说  你想要和我联手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我们有一起生活过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样也不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有和你同样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你所封印的Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能得到研究数据
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能操控更多的Phantom了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有一点没明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的确拥有从我身上夺走的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是会成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马加锡亚  克苏鲁  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上  马加锡亚  克苏鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了各位  反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区几个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马加锡亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束吧  enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神振之力  phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于托托天伦中显其虚像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类也挺行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让phantom知道人类也是有可取之处的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  你成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露  你变回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久瑠美  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特也辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来  晴彦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书你一直都带着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都已经忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  这是第一本让你热衷的书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  我和妈妈真正意义上的重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要隐藏事实的阿赖耶识社
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会被追究严重的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夺走特异能力的人们也都恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好没劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然会是晴彦的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是一部分  其实更像是双胞胎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  你们本来就是一体的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双胞胎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖  你就叫我姐姐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当我姐姐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也交换了贴纸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会分小糸姐姐一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你要哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  那本图书上也有个像露露这样的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  快来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的委托有点棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但相信你们应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们愿意接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从人类的脑中所诞生出的真实的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们生活在这幻想与现实暧昧不清的不安定世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却格外喜欢这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
